<i>noun</i>: 고행 [고행] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>고행 [고행]</dt><br>
<dd>1. penance; asceticism; mortification</dd><br>
<dd>불교에서, 몸으로 견디기 어려운 일들을 통하여 수행을 쌓는 일.</dd><br>
<dd>In Buddhism, an act of making oneself suffer physically, with an intention to suppress one's desire and find illumination.</dd><br>
<dd>2. suffering</dd><br>
<dd>(비유적으로) 힘들고 괴로운 일을 겪음.</dd><br>
<dd>(figurative) An act of going through a difficult and agonizing incident.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>